{"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0,"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyO5UPnpZu1o1z233PRPVsLk"},"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Task 1\n","    - Create a function that would swap the value of x and y using only x and y as variables.\n","    - x and y must be numeric.\n","    - Return -1 if x and y is not numeric, and\n","    - print the swapped values if both x and y are numeric."],"metadata":{"id":"gb_4qvQ_UCtO"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["def swap_values(x, y):\n","    # Check if both values are numeric\n","    if not (isinstance(x, (int, float)) and isinstance(y, (int, float))):\n","        return -1\n","        # Swap using arithmetic operations without any temporary variable\n","    x = x + y\n","    y = x - y\n","    x = x - y\n","\n","    print(\"Swapped values:\")\n","    print(\"x =\", x)\n","    print(\"y =\", y)\n","    return (x, y)\n","\n","\n","\n","\n","\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"QhFXeYTrR1tP","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1745440724928,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":7,"user":{"displayName":"Herrudin Shamsudin","userId":"00573043848249318364"}}},"execution_count":33,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Task 2\n"," Invoke the function \"swap\" using the following scenarios:\n"," - \"Apple\", 10\n"," - 9, 17"],"metadata":{"id":"KExCglCZUh0t"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["print(\"Result for ('Apple', 10):\", swap(\"Apple\", 10))\n","print(\"Result for (9, 17):\", swap(9, 17))"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"Y6Zy-EgKU37c","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1745439958152,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":11,"user":{"displayName":"Herrudin Shamsudin","userId":"00573043848249318364"}},"outputId":"2064b935-2979-4328-ef72-6bfa10fd5d70"},"execution_count":9,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Result for ('Apple', 10): -1\n","Result for (9, 17): None\n"]}]}]}